SUMMARY:Stafford Lake Social (MUST READ DESCRIPTION)
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\nPlease read carefully—there’s no c
 ell reception\, so plan ahead! 😊\nWe’ll meet at Group Area 1 or 2 (de
 pending on table availability). Turn right when you enter the park—parki
 ng will be on the left. Bring a chair or blanket just in case.\nIf we’re
  in Area 1\, cross the small bridge past the volleyball net to find us.\nN
 ote: No dogs allowed. Restrooms are nearby!\nRSVP counts may look off sinc
 e this is cross-posted.\nThis is a laid-back meetup—do whatever you want
 ! Bring games\, sporting goods\, art supplies\, food for yourself or to sh
 are (optional)\, or just relax. There’s volleyball\, and hammocks are lo
 cated at the other end of the park if you want to lounge.\nLooking forward
  to fresh air and good company! 🌿✨
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/sonoma-marin-brat-pack/events/3141398
