SUMMARY:Do whatever you want !
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\nHey everyone! As the weather turns col
 der and rainier\, it’s the perfect excuse to stay cozy indoors 😊\nLet
 ’s hang out\, stay dry\, and enjoy some board games together! Feel free 
 to bring any games you love. Not into gaming? No worries at all—bring an
  art project or something creative you enjoy.\nThis spot has tons of tasty
  food and treats (one of my regular favorites!)\, so come hungry if you’
 d like. And if you’re just in the mood to relax and not do much\, that
 ’s totally fine too—this is a laid-back\, go-with-the-flow kind of gat
 hering.\nWe’ll grab whatever seating we can\, so if you don’t see us u
 p front\, check toward the back. Looking forward to seeing you there!\n\n*
 **Please note this event is cross posted with other groups so the number o
 f RSVPs might not reflect the actual number of people attending.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/sonoma-marin-brat-pack/events/3141663
 06/
